  "title": "Marketing Associate (Travel Opportunities)",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for individuals who are curious, driven, and open to growth. This role offers a structured pathway to develop professional and leadership skills through real responsibilities, close mentorship, and hands-on experience.</p><p>If you’re looking for meaningful work, clear progression, and exposure beyond a desk role, this could be a good fit.<br /></p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Participate in a structured training programme designed for long-term growth</li><li>Work alongside experienced mentors</li><li>Develop skills in communication, planning, and team coordination</li><li>Take on increasing responsibility as you progress</li><li>Contribute to projects that support business expansion and operations</li></ul><p><br /><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>1-to-1 Mentorship</li><li>Leadership Development Opportunities</li><li>Regional Exposure & Travel Opportunities</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><p>We believe good careers are built, not rushed. Here, you’ll gain real skills, real guidance, and the opportunity to grow at a pace that reflects your effort and contribution.</p><p><em>If you’re ready to grow, travel, and be mentored — we’d love to meet you.</em></p>",
